<br />

<br />
The only classes with pets who cant snare/root are mages and BST - all others have one or both or better(mess) --- we dont have it because mages dont - but everyone else does -- why is it ok for necros, druid and chanters to root/snare with a pet/charmed pet/DC pet and not ok for the main pet classes? Remember that those other classes used to not have pets at all back when mages were denied root/snare. Now they have the pets but not the CC issue.
<br />

<br />
