<br />

<br />
1) the lack of equiptment from VT up to the plane of fire. We have very few items with BST on them and most we fight with Monks for (and we lose on most of them in many guilds) and alot of all/all stuff thats inferior to class specifc items.  Its sad but cloth robes in VT are better in ac and other stats than what BST can wear, leather or all/all, by far.
<br />

<br />
